  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then after two years, it was-- had been agreed with him and my father that after two years I would be sent to school in Dreisen, the European Fashion Academy, where I would then be trained to complete the technical training that I had gotten.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And by this time it was 1933.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "In fact, I left on the 1st of April 1933.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I left Hildsheim for Dreisen, and that was the day of the boycott day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "That was the first widely anti-Semitic activity by the Nazis, where every store, every law practice, every medical practice was boycotted by having storm troopers standing at the entrance and discouraging people from going into a medical practice, to this Jewish doctor, or going into our store, or other stores that were Jewishly owned.",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I remember that my father and mother both were very happy that I would not be home on that day, not realizing that by the time I got to Dreisen all by myself and alone that I saw it in Dreisen.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that was the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I think it was the beginning when I started to realize that the-- we had made for-- ever since Hitler came to power on the 30th of January 1933, we had made it about-- in wishful thinking.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember my father saying, you know, let this idiot show them how he can run the country.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he will not be able to, and therefore in a couple of months, it will be all over.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he will be kicked out by the people that behind him and the big industrialists who were right-wing industrialists, and-- and they will not last.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
